Text: I started downloading this one but fortunately had a quick look into it - unfortunately, the lady in this image set is NOT Dorothy Black (former PLAYBOY Playmate of some month in 2002 or 2003, real name Dora Meszaros), but far less known (and far less breasted...) Monica Sweet (aka Jo, Juliana Sage, real name Monica Nagy).The only thing these two ladies have in common is their nationality, Hungary. Kind regards, errors are just human.
